{"type": "article", "id": 13900, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-08-24T08:05:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8224, "name": "手拿包"}, {"id": 14921, "name": "三明治机"}, {"id": 14922, "name": "创意家居"}, {"id": 3149, "name": "灯具"}, {"id": 14923, "name": "视频辅助设备"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 14924, "name": "Ogilvy & Mather"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606154018lWkEIq93opJN4GHh.png", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tVIW by Frankly\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Frankly 是一家来自瑞典的公司，这是他们最近推出的一款视频辅助设备，它被安装在手机摄像头上，可以把视频的画面扩大 50％，同时，在光照不足的条件下可以自动调整照明环境，自动补光，并且不会对画面质量造成伤害，从而为视频带来更为舒适的体验。它适用于所有的电脑和智能移动端，通过蓝牙和设备进行连接，使用 USB 充电。<a href=\"http://www.getaviw.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203016ycb6J4ultF5pYaE8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55867971\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203017NL14P50tfDwHmCTl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203017I6gC1BYshqp4FbZ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203018FqXerbGHfm5dBDux.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203018u5MmTYN8n1D2I0RE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060520301858BsbWXNodxItD70.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052030195s0j7SRHfgtvTbK2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75427873\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tKihou by Tangent Design\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是英国设计工作室 Tangent Design 最近推出的一款特别的灯具，他们把粘稠的物质填充在陶瓷容器里面，顶部是黑色硅油薄膜，底部是 LED 灯泡，当小水泵把空气送上去，发光的气泡也会随之升上去，实现了金色气泡闪动的效果，结合黑色的背景色，看上去非常神秘和庄严。 Tangent Design 一直以来以特殊的照明设计著名，<a href=\"http://www.tangent.uk.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看他们更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203020MlwfEIjgVx8CYPFW.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6601467\" data-format=\"gif\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060520302173dASnWkQZlpCYJT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203021CynBd8tMiLNZKk2D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203022cRBtKnsPADx6Fdwi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203022s4MI2HpXN9ZGOR0g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203023lSOuNHZm59w6Bd2T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203023F5sZmX6fcrdkTRqg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t“Air Max 95” by Ogilvy &amp; Mather\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>今年是 Nike 经典的 Air Max 95 系列的 20 周年纪念，为了配合纪念活动，Ogilvy &amp; Mather 试图重现这个经典系列：他们把 Air Max 95 系列球鞋图案画成了一张张卡片，制作成限量版的游戏卡，并放在 Nike 门店的自动售货机里面，投入硬币即可得到。此外，他们还制作了一部分纯手工的卡片，当幸运的人得到这样的卡片，可以获得限量版耐克运动鞋或者 Air Max 95 系列运动鞋。而其中还有最最稀有的金属手绘耐克 ID 卡，得到卡的人可以获得定制一双球鞋的机会。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203024yp8ogl7WmVqKdf5b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203025dgw6sTrOjJNnYi81.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203025fJRn2deEj3SwxDCI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203026TOW8Ig7HVMB1QRcx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203026a4US9bjC5lQ0xBkX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203027hs7wcTnPUm6Yi5r9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203027KqcYN6dxmgLfZOs2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203028rIQOmC0pDdh2VEX7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203028iWh6N5LGZBStAxjr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203029estwlFuMEJBXT1rN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tConfluentia By Bina Baitel Studio\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是来自 Bina Baitel Studio 设计工作室的一套创意家居产品，其中一款是一个和挂毯连接在一起的床头柜，另外一款是一个和地毯连接在一起的双床头柜。绿色的“瀑布”从床头柜上流出，进入用户的房间，像是开了一扇窗，进入另外的一片风光。尽管这个配色实在是让人想吐槽太过于焦虑，但是从创意来看，或许会有所启发。<a href=\"http://www.binabaitel.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看工作室其他作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203030Zt16IGxK9Vu8Tbi3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47916667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203030lGta5vHximr0WCVF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203031yxeLTo9YRUDdCg3A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69479167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203031dTh4UnMeGSZNXH0m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60208333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tSandwich Maker by Polar\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>户外运动品牌 Poler 最近推出了一款便利烤三明治机，方便用户在户外烤三明治、火腿等食物，只需要把食材放进模具里面，然后放置在火上烤，便可以轻松制作健康的三明治，为户外活动中食物的制作提供了便利。目前售价 53 美元，<a href=\"http://www.polerstuff.com/products/the-poler-sandwich-maker?variant=3815163588\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203032mhJyx7WRGeTj84oI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203032VLpf0IvsioRlz2kr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203032rqb6fFD3MZzn10v5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56445312\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203033WFPCmSKvMziI2Xp7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203034pfVs3xlHcWAouPwJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203034aDXZco8swBh9nJpt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203034W6m9igSH072ocTyC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tLipstick Clutch by Tom Ford \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Tom Ford 最近推出了一款非常贴心的手拿包，他们在里面做了一个专门放置口红或唇膏的小暗格，解决了晚会中常常遇到的手忙脚乱翻口红的问题，同时，里面还有拉链小袋子和卡片格子，分工非常明确到位。除了“务实”的里子，它外观上却是金光闪闪，看上去蛮高调。这是<a href=\"http://www.net-a-porter.com/Shop/Designers/Tom_Ford/Bags?pn=1&amp;npp=60&amp;image_view=product&amp;dScroll=0&amp;cm_mmc=LinkshareUS-_-JlFzVGPAZUQ-_-Custom-_-LinkBuilder&amp;siteID=JlFzVGPAZUQ-CEolHi6lW.uu9z_9UXCIsQ\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052030357GN6pJ0VOtfUiTSw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203036bURxBPuzDCMAoh45.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203036QYqvrewfVX5yC0gN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}